assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Toyo Shutter Co., Ltd. manufactures, installs, purchases, imports, sells, and exports various shutters, and building fixtures, materials, and consumables in Japan. It provides weight, lightweight, aluminum, madrimo, and high speed sheet shutters; over, hanger, steel, entrance, and special doors; residential overdoors; shutter blinds; lever handles; holding gates; and radio systems, as well as building fine exterior wall renovation services. The company also offers architectural hardware, marine equipment/decorative hardware, and furniture and kitchen equipment, as well as disaster, crime, and flood prevention equipment. In addition, it engages in the design, supervision, contracting, and execution of construction and facility construction; design and construction of electrical equipment work; development of computer software; sale of computer equipment; sale, installation, and repair of machinery, equipment, and materials for various types of electric transportation and electrical equipment; and buying, selling, leasing, brokerage, and management of real estate. Further, the company is involved in outdoor advertising; maintenance work; industrial and intangible property rights business, such as copyrights, know-how, system engineering, acquisition, rental, and sale of other software; non-life insurance agency business; automobile liability insurance agency business; and business related to solicitation of life insurance. Toyo Shutter Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 1955 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan.
